"documentation/business-messaging/whatsapp/business-phone-numbers/phone-"
"numbers>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Meta for Developers：新增電話號碼 <https://developers.facebook.com/"
"documentation/business-messaging/whatsapp/business-phone-numbers/phone-"
"numbers>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:440
msgid "Create a permanent token"
msgstr "建立永久權杖"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:442
msgid ""
"After configuration and testing are complete, create a permanent token to "
"replace the :guilabel:`Temporary token`."
msgstr "完成配置和測試後，建立永久權杖以取代\\ :guilabel:`臨時權杖`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:446
msgid ""
"`Meta for Developers: System User Access Tokens <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/business-management-api/get-"
"started#system-user- access-tokens>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Meta for Developers：系統使用者存取權杖 <https://developers.facebook.com/"
"docs/whatsapp/business-management-api/get-started#system-user- access-tokens>"
"`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:450
msgid ""
"Navigate to `Meta Business Suite <https://business.facebook.com/>`__ and "
"then go to :menuselection:`Business settings --> User --> System Users`. "
"Select an existing system user or create a new system user by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"前往 `Meta Business Suite <https://business.facebook.com/>`__，然後前往\\ "
":menuselection:`商家設定 --> 使用者 --> 系統使用者`\\ 。選擇現有的系統使用者"
"或按一下\\ :guilabel:`加入`\\ 建立新的系統使用者。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:454
msgid ""
"To generate a permanent token, assets must be added to the system user. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add assets`, and a pop-up window appears. "
"Select :guilabel:`Apps` under :guilabel:`Select asset type`, then select the "
"`Odoo` app and toggle the permissions to :guilabel:`On` under "
"the :guilabel:`Full control` option, then click :guilabel:`Save Changes`. "
"Click :guilabel:`Done` in the confirmation window that appears."
msgstr ""
"若要產生永久權杖，必須將資產加入到系統使用者。按一下\\ :guilabel:`加入資產`\\"
" ，就會出現彈出式視窗。在\\ :guilabel:`選擇資產類型`\\ 下選擇\\ :guilabel:`應"
"用程式`\\ ，然後選擇 `Odoo` 應用程式，並在\\ :guilabel:`完全控制`\\ 選項下將"
"權限切換為\\ :guilabel:`開啟`\\ ，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`儲存變更`\\ 。在出"
"現的確認視窗中按一下\\ :guilabel:`完成`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:460
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Generate new token`, and a pop-up window appears asking "
"which app this token should be generated for. Select the `Odoo` app, then "
"set the expiration date to either :guilabel:`60 days` or :guilabel:`Never`."
msgstr ""
"按一下\\ :guilabel:`產生新權杖`\\ ，就會出現彈出式視窗，詢問應該為哪個應用程"
"式產生此權杖。選擇 `Odoo` 應用程式，然後將到期日設定為\\ :guilabel:`60 天`\\ "
"或\\ :guilabel:`永不`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:464
msgid ""
"Meta asks which permissions the system user allows. Add both of the "
"following permissions:"
msgstr "Meta 會詢問系統使用者允許哪些權限。加入以下兩個權限："

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:466
msgid "`business_management`"
msgstr "`business_management`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:467
msgid "`whatsapp_business_messaging`"
msgstr "`whatsapp_business_messaging`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:468
msgid "`whatsapp_business_management`"
msgstr "`whatsapp_business_management`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:469
msgid "`whatsapp_business_manage_events`"
msgstr "`whatsapp_business_manage_events`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:471
msgid ""
"When permissions are set, click :guilabel:`Generate token`. Copy the token "
"value that populates on the screen that follows."
msgstr "設定權限後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`產生權杖`\\ 。複製後續畫面上顯示的權杖值。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:474
msgid ""
"With that token value, update the :guilabel:`Access Token` field in the "
"WhatsApp business account in Odoo by navigating to :menuselection:`WhatsApp "
"app --> Configuration --> WhatsApp Business Accounts`."
msgstr ""
"使用該權杖值，前往\\ :menuselection:`WhatsApp 應用程式 --> 配置 --> WhatsApp "
"企業帳戶`\\ ，更新 Odoo 中 WhatsApp 企業帳戶的\\ :guilabel:`存取權杖`\\ 欄位"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:481
msgid "Go live with the Meta app"
msgstr "讓 Meta 應用程式上線"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:483
msgid ""
"Finally, to launch the app, the Meta app must be set to :guilabel:`Live` in "
"the `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__. "
"Click the app that is being configured, then toggle the :guilabel:`App Mode` "
"field from :guilabel:`Development` to :guilabel:`Live`."
msgstr ""
"最後，若要啟動應用程式，必須在 `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ 中將 Meta 應用程式設定為\\ :guilabel:`上"
"線`\\ 。按一下正在配置的應用程式，然後將\\ :guilabel:`應用程式模式`\\ 欄位"
"從\\ :guilabel:`開發`\\ 切換到\\ :guilabel:`上線`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:488
msgid ""
"If the app status is **not** set to *live*, then the database is only able "
"to contact the test numbers specified in the developer console."
msgstr ""
"如果應用程式狀態**未**設定為*上線*，則資料庫只能聯絡開發者控制台中指定的測試"
"號碼。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:492
msgid ""
"A privacy policy URL must be set in order for the app to be set to live. Go "
"to the `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ "
"and select the `Odoo` app. Then, in the left-hand side menu, go "
"to :menuselection:`App Settings --> Basic`. Enter the privacy policy "
"hyperlink address under the :guilabel:`Privacy Policy URL` field of the "
"form. Click :guilabel:`Save changes` to apply the privacy policy to the app."
msgstr ""
"必須設定隱私權政策網址，應用程式才能設定為上線。前往 `Meta Developer "
"Dashboard <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ 並選擇 `Odoo` 應用程式。"
"然後，在左側選單中，前往\\ :menuselection:`應用程式設定 --> 基本`\\ 。在表單"
"的\\ :guilabel:`隱私權政策網址`\\ 欄位下輸入隱私權政策超連結地址。按一下\\ "
":guilabel:`儲存變更`\\ 將隱私權政策套用到應用程式。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:498
msgid ""
"Once the app has gone live in the Meta developer console, a confirmation "
"email is sent to the administrator."
msgstr "應用程式在 Meta 開發者控制台上線後，系統會傳送確認電子郵件給管理員。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:504
msgid "WhatsApp templates"
msgstr "WhatsApp 範本"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:506
msgid ""
"WhatsApp templates allow users to store messages that are frequently sent. "
"By creating templates tailored to specific situations, users can send pre-"
"approved messages, without having to compromise on quality or compose the "
"same text repeatedly. This ensures fast turnaround and consistent customer "
"service messaging, and increases the overall engagement rate with the "
"customer."
msgstr ""
"WhatsApp 範本允許使用者儲存經常傳送的訊息。透過建立針對特定情況量身打造的範本"
"，使用者可以傳送預先核准的訊息，而無需在品質上妥協或重複撰寫相同的文字。這確"
"保了快速的周轉時間和一致的客戶服務訊息，並提高了與客戶的整體互動率。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:511
msgid ""
"WhatsApp templates can be created on both the :ref:`Odoo <whatsapp/odoo-"
"templates>` and :ref:`Meta <whatsapp/meta-templates>` consoles."
msgstr ""
"WhatsApp 範本可以在\\ :ref:`Odoo <whatsapp/odoo-templates>`\\ 和\\ "
":ref:`Meta <whatsapp/meta-templates>`\\ 控制台上建立。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:515
msgid ""
"WhatsApp has an approval process that **must** be completed *before* the "
"template can be used. See :ref:`productivity/whatsapp/template-approval`."
msgstr ""
"WhatsApp 有一個核准流程，**必須**在範本使用*之前*完成。請參閱\\ "
":ref:`productivity/whatsapp/template-approval`。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:518
msgid ""
"To access WhatsApp templates, navigate to the :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --"
"> Templates` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"若要存取 WhatsApp 範本，請前往\\ :menuselection:`WhatsApp 應用程式 --> 範"
"本`\\ Dashboard。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:520
msgid "Each template has three tabs:"
msgstr "每個範本都有三個分頁："

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:522
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Body`\\: stores the message body. The message body may contain "
"placeholders for dynamic content which is populated when the message is sent."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`內文`：儲存訊息內文。訊息內文可包含動態內容的占位符，在傳送訊息時"
"填入實際內容。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:524
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Buttons`\\: adds clickable buttons/hyperlinks at the bottom of "
"the WhatsApp template. Currently, there are three button types\\: *Quick "
"Reply*, *Visit Website*, and *Call Number*. *Visit Website* supports static, "
"dynamic, and tracked URLs."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`按鈕`：在 WhatsApp 範本底部加入可點擊的按鈕或超連結。目前有三種按"
"鈕類型：*快速回覆*、*造訪網站*和*撥打電話*。*造訪網站*支援靜態、動態和追蹤網"
"址。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:527
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Variables`\\: lists all of the placeholders in the template, as "
"well as the variables that should be populated. For example, messages can "
"contain placeholders for a recipient's name, purchased products, or sales "
"order number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`變數`：列出範本中的所有占位符以及應填入的變數。例如，訊息可包含收"
"件人姓名、已購產品或銷售單編號的占位符。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:534
msgid "Create WhatsApp templates in Odoo"
msgstr "在 Odoo 中建立 WhatsApp 範本"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:536
msgid ""
"To create a WhatsApp template, go to the :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> "
"Templates` dashboard and click :guilabel:`New`. Enter a :guilabel:`Name` for "
"the template, and select a :guilabel:`Language`."
msgstr ""
"若要建立 WhatsApp 範本，請前往\\ :menuselection:`WhatsApp 應用程式 ‣ 範本`\\ "
"的 Dashboard 並按一下\\ :guilabel:`新增`。輸入範本的\\ :guilabel:`名稱`，並選"
"擇\\ :guilabel:`語言`。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:540
msgid ""
"In order to complete this next task, :doc:`administrator access rights <../"
"general/users/access_rights>` are needed to edit the :guilabel:`Applies to` "
"field."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:543
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Account` drop-down menu, select the *WhatsApp business "
"account* in Odoo that this template should link to. Next, under "
"the :guilabel:`Applies to` field, select the *model* the server action "
"should apply to this template."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :guilabel:`帳戶`\\ 下拉選單中，選擇此範本應連結的 Odoo *WhatsApp 企業帳"
"戶*。接下來，在\\ :guilabel:`適用於`\\ 欄位中，選擇伺服器動作應套用此範本"
"的*模型*。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:548
msgid ""
"These models can also be accessed in :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`. "
"In a contact form (or similar relevant form in Odoo), navigate to the model "
"to be referenced, and hover over a field name. This displays backend "
"information, including the specific Odoo :guilabel:`Model` name in the "
"backend. Search for the model's *frontend* name in the WhatsApp template, "
"under the :guilabel:`Applies to` drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"這些模型也可以在\\ :ref:`開發人員模式 <developer-mode>`\\ 中訪問。在聯絡人表"
"單（或 Odoo 中類似的相關表單）中，導航至要參考的模型，並將滑鼠懸停在欄位名稱"
"上。這會顯示後端資訊，包括後端中特定的 Odoo :guilabel:`模型`\\ 名稱。在 "
"WhatsApp 範本中的\\ :guilabel:`適用於`\\ 下拉式選單下搜尋模型的*前端*名稱。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:555
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Phone Field` may produce an error when changing the model "
"or :guilabel:`Applies to` field. The :guilabel:`Phone Field` should always "
"be set to the `Phone` or `Mobile` model."
msgstr ""
"變更模型或\\ :guilabel:`適用於`\\ 欄位時，:guilabel:`電話欄位`\\ 可能會產生錯"
"誤。:guilabel:`電話欄位`\\ 應始終設定為「電話」或「行動電話」模型。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:558
msgid ""
"To search available fields, type the frontend name in "
"the :guilabel:`Search...` box. This displays results from all of the "
"available fields for the model (:guilabel:`Applies to`) that the template is "
"created for."
msgstr ""
"若要搜尋可用欄位，請在\\ :guilabel:`搜尋...`\\ 方塊中輸入前端名稱。這會顯示為"
"範本建立的模型（:guilabel:`適用於`）的所有可用欄位的結果。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:563
msgid ""
"To find specific fields, multiple levels may need to be navigated in the "
"search results box. Use the :icon:`fa-chevron-right` :guilabel:`(right "
"chevron)` and :icon:`fa-arrow-left` :guilabel:`(left arrow)` icons to "
"navigate between the menu levels."
msgstr ""
"若要尋找特定欄位，可能需要在搜尋結果方塊中導航多個層級。使用\\ :icon:`fa-"
"chevron-right` :guilabel:`（右箭頭）`\\ 和\\ :icon:`fa-arrow-left` "
":guilabel:`（左箭頭）`\\ 圖示在選單層級之間導航。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid "Searching for the phone field in the search bar."
msgstr "在搜尋列中搜尋電話欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:570
msgid "Change the :guilabel:`Category` to one of the following:"
msgstr "將\\ :guilabel:`類別`\\ 變更為以下其中一項："

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:572
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:775
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Marketing`: Promotions or information about the business, "
"products or services. Or any message that is not utility or authentication."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`行銷`：關於業務、產品或服務的促銷或資訊。或任何非實用或驗證的訊息"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:574
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:777
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Utility`: Messages about a specific transaction, account, order "
"or customer request."
msgstr ":guilabel:`實用`：關於特定交易、帳戶、訂單或客戶請求的訊息。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:575
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:778
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Authentication`: One-time passwords that customers use to "
"authenticate a transaction or login."
msgstr ":guilabel:`驗證`：客戶用於驗證交易或登入的一次性密碼。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:579
msgid ""
"Specifying an incorrect category can cause a flag/rejected status from Meta "
"during the approval process."
msgstr "指定錯誤的類別可能會導致 Meta 在審核過程中標記為旗標或遭拒狀態。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:582
msgid ""
"Add any :guilabel:`Users` that are allowed to use this template. In the "
"right-side column, a :guilabel:`Header type` can be configured along with "
"a :guilabel:`Header message`, as well."
msgstr ""
"加入任何允許使用此範本的\\ :guilabel:`使用者`。在右側欄位中，還可以配置\\ "
":guilabel:`頁首類型`\\ 以及\\ :guilabel:`頁首訊息`。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:585
msgid "The available :guilabel:`Header types` are as follows:"
msgstr "可用的\\ :guilabel:`頁首類型`\\ 如下："

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:588
msgid "Image"
msgstr "圖片"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:589
msgid "Video"
msgstr "影片"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:590
msgid "Document"
msgstr "文件"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:591
msgid "Location (variables need to be set)"
msgstr "位置（需要設定變數）"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:593
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :guilabel:`Body` tab to configure the main message of the "
"template."
msgstr "導航至\\ :guilabel:`內容`\\ 分頁以配置範本的主要訊息。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:595
msgid ""
"When all the necessary changes are made to the template, click "
"the :guilabel:`Submit for approval` button in the upper-left corner, and the "
"status of the template changes to :guilabel:`Pending`."
msgstr ""
"完成範本的所有必要變更後，按一下左上角的\\ :guilabel:`提交審核`\\ 按鈕，範本"
"的狀態將變更為\\ :guilabel:`待處理`。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:598
msgid ""
"The status remains :guilabel:`Pending` until a decision has been made by "
"Meta, whereby a confirmation email is sent indicating that the template has "
"been approved or rejected. Next, sync the templates from the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"狀態將保持\\ :guilabel:`待處理`，直到 Meta 做出決定，屆時會傳送確認電子郵件，"
"說明範本已獲核准或被拒絕。接著，從 Odoo 資料庫同步範本。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:603
msgid ":ref:`Syncing templates <productivity/whatsapp/sync-templates>`"
msgstr ":ref:`同步範本 <productivity/whatsapp/sync-templates>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:606
msgid ""
"Preconfigured demo data templates are available in Odoo to use or modify. "
"These templates can be used as-is or modified to suit a specific business "
"need."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 中提供預先配置的示範資料範本以供使用或修改。這些範本可以按原樣使用或修改"
"以適合特定的業務需求。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:609
msgid ""
"To use these templates, navigate to :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> "
"Templates` and select a preconfigured template. Click :guilabel:`Submit for "
"Approval` to start the approval process. An email is sent to the "
"administrator of the Meta account when the template has been approved."
msgstr ""
"若要使用這些範本，請前往\\ :menuselection:`WhatsApp 應用程式 --> 範本`\\ 並選"
"擇預先配置的範本。按一下\\ :guilabel:`提交核准`\\ 以開始核准流程。當範本已核"
"准時，將向 Meta 帳戶的管理員傳送電子郵件。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:616
msgid "Buttons"
msgstr "按鈕"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:618
msgid ""
"Buttons can be added into the message from the :guilabel:`Buttons` tab. "
"Enter the :guilabel:`Type` (either :guilabel:`Visit "
"Website`, :guilabel:`Call Number`, or :guilabel:`Quick Reply`), and then "
"specify the :guilabel:`Button Text`, :guilabel:`Call Number` "
"or :guilabel:`Website URL` (including :guilabel:`Url Type`), depending on "
"the :guilabel:`Type` of button."
msgstr ""
"可以從\\ :guilabel:`按鈕`\\ 分頁將按鈕加入訊息中。輸入\\ :guilabel:`類型`（可"
"為\\ :guilabel:`訪問網站`、:guilabel:`撥打號碼`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`快速回覆`）"
"，然後根據按鈕的\\ :guilabel:`類型`\\ 指定\\ :guilabel:`按鈕文"
"字`、:guilabel:`撥打號碼`\\ 或\\ :guilabel:`網站網址`（包括\\ :guilabel:`網址"
"類型`）。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:624
msgid ""
"Buttons can also be added on the `Meta Business Suite <https://"
"business.facebook.com/wa/manage/home>`__. To see Meta's WhatsApp template "
"dashboard, go to :menuselection:`Account tools --> Message templates`."
msgstr ""
"按鈕也可以在 `Meta Business Suite <https://business.facebook.com/wa/manage/"
"home>`__ 上加入。若要查看 Meta 的 WhatsApp 範本 Dashboard，請前往\\ "
":menuselection:`帳戶工具 ‣ 訊息範本`。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:631
msgid "Placeholders and variables"
msgstr "占位符和變數"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:633
msgid ""
"Dynamic variables reference certain fields within the Odoo database to "
"produce unique data in the WhatsApp message when using a template. Dynamic "
"variables are encoded to display fields from within the database, "
"referencing fields from within a model."
msgstr ""
"動態變數引用 Odoo 資料庫中的特定欄位，以便在使用範本時在 WhatsApp 訊息中產生"
"唯一資料。動態變數經過編碼以顯示資料庫中的欄位，從模型中引用欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:638
msgid ""
"Many companies like to customize their WhatsApp messages with a personalized "
"piece of customer information to grab attention. This can be accomplished in "
"Odoo by referencing a field within a model by setting a dynamic variable. "
"For example, a customer's name can be referenced in the email from "
"the :guilabel:`Customer` field on the :guilabel:`Sales Order` model."
msgstr ""
"許多公司喜歡使用個人化的客戶資訊來自訂其 WhatsApp 訊息以吸引注意。在 Odoo 中"
"可以透過設定動態變數來引用模型中的欄位來實現這一點。例如，可以從\\ "
":guilabel:`銷售單`\\ 模型上的\\ :guilabel:`合作夥伴`\\ 欄位在電子郵件中引用客"
"戶的姓名。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:None
msgid "WhatsApp message with dynamic variables highlighted."
msgstr "突出顯示動態變數的 WhatsApp 訊息。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:646
msgid ""
"Dynamic variables can be added in to the :guilabel:`Body` by "
"adding :guilabel:`placeholders` in the *text*. To add a placeholder in the "
"*message body* enter the following text `{{1}}`. For the second placeholder "
"enter `{{2}}` and increase incrementally as more placeholders are added to "
"the text."
msgstr ""
"可以透過在*文字*中加入\\ :guilabel:`佔位符`\\ 將動態變數加入\\ :guilabel:`內"
"容`\\ 中。要在*訊息內容*中加入佔位符，請輸入以下文字 `{{1}}`。對於第二個佔位"
"符，輸入 `{{2}}`，隨著更多佔位符加入文字，遞增編號。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:651
msgid "*The following is the text from payment receipt template body:*"
msgstr "*以下是付款收據範本內容的文字：*"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:653
msgid "Dear {{1}},"
msgstr "親愛的 {{1}}："

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:0
msgid "Here is your invoice *{{2}}* from *{{3}}* for a total of *{{4}}{{5}}*."
msgstr "這是您的發票 *{{2}}*，來自 *{{3}}*，總金額為 *{{4}}{{5}}*。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:0
msgid "To review your invoice or pay online: {{6}}"
msgstr "查看您的發票或線上付款：{{6}}"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:658
msgid "Thank you"
msgstr "謝謝"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:661
msgid ":ref:`productivity/whatsapp/templates`"
msgstr ":ref:`productivity/whatsapp/templates`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:663
msgid ""
"These placeholders **must** be configured on the :guilabel:`Variables` tab "
"of the template before submitting for approval from Meta. To edit the "
"dynamic variables on a template, first change the :guilabel:`Type` "
"to :guilabel:`Field of Model`. This allows Odoo to reference a field within "
"a model to produce unique data in the message being sent."
msgstr ""
"在向 Meta 提交審核之前，**必須**在範本的\\ :guilabel:`變數`\\ 分頁上配置這些"
"占位符。若要編輯範本上的動態變數，請先將\\ :guilabel:`類型`\\ 變更為\\ "
":guilabel:`模型欄位`。這樣可以讓 Odoo 參照模型中的欄位，以在傳送的訊息中產生"
"唯一資料。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:668
msgid ""
"Next, edit the :guilabel:`Field` of the dynamic variables. "
"The :guilabel:`Applies to` field in the template should be edited prior to "
"ensure the correct model and field are referenced."
msgstr ""
"接下來，編輯動態變數的\\ :guilabel:`欄位`。應事先編輯範本中的\\ :guilabel:`適"
"用於`\\ 欄位，以確保引用正確的模型和欄位。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:671
msgid ""
"To search the available fields, type in the front-end name of the field in "
"the search box. This finds a result from all of the available fields for the "
"model (:guilabel:`Applies to`) that the template is created for. There may "
"be multiple levels that need to be configured."
msgstr ""
"若要搜尋可用欄位，請在搜尋方塊中輸入欄位的前端名稱。這會從為範本建立的模型"
"（:guilabel:`適用於`）的所有可用欄位中找到結果。可能需要配置多個層級。"

